<li>(editor and contributor) <i>Conflict After the Cold War: Arguments on Causes of War and Peace</i> (New York: Allyn &amp; Bacon, 1994)</li>
<li>(co-editor with Thomas Mahnken, and contributor) <i>Paradoxes of Strategic Intelligence: Essays in Honor of Michael I. Handel</i> (London: Frank Cass, 2003)</li>
